      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "算小奶狗类型的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦，你觉得你不是小奶狗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "完全不是...",
