      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "我杭州的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "杭州好啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "我同学也有好多杭州的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "我喜欢吃西湖醋鱼和芭比馒头",
