      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "你味觉失灵了，还是搞抽象了？",
