      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是巴比馒头真的还可以",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "我为芭比馒头发声！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "，本来想说你刻板印象的",
