      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "看在巴比馒头的份上就算了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "那真是谢谢你我的包容",
