      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我蛮喜欢这个梗的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我刚好教的是汉语言文学",
