      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "余华不也会用这些字吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我普普通通一个大学老师 对文学的追求再高能高得过余华吗？",
