      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯没什么光环，也没什么特别的讲究。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你这是在立人设吗？",
